      "tips": "Selena summons an Abyssal Devil to lurk in a designated location. The Abyssal Devil smothers a nearby enemy with its body. Within several seconds, the enemy’s movement speed is reduced. After some time, this skill deals damage to the target and other nearby enemies, slows enemies for several seconds. Selena can summon up to 3 Abyssal Devils. Damage will decay when a target takes damage from multiple devils at the same time.",
